{"tid":2195913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身為女人係香港一定要好好保護自己","createTime":"2020-09-09T13:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T15:00:15.000Z","uid":6783,"like":52,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2554d1f28837d253ff137e30c6e986b27124de","tid":2195913,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"我今日就食雲呑麵 <br />\n點知搭枱嗰個阿叔話我對筷子揸得唔啱<br />\n仲隊佢嗰對筷子去我臉前話教我<br />\n仲不停咁嘆氣話 唉  依家啲後生連筷子都揸唔啱<br />\n一開始都算 我忍佢<br />\n點知越食佢就越講 仲望住我喺度唉唉聲<br />\n我就話 你再係咁我就唔客氣<br />\n跟住佢就話 唏 你d後生女做到d咩<br />\n咁我梗係好嬲啦 細細聲同佢講 你玩完了<br />\n之後我就大嗌 非禮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個阿叔非禮我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢即刻比店員欄住 有幾個後生仔幫我禁住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教我揸筷子啊拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身敗名裂啦你"},{"pid":"c8bcf3fb58ac7bd86de9660188f70170438a4b8f","tid":2195913,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHo ball"},{"pid":"b1e0370efc256057cef38a306d1d42b7aa804891","tid":2195913,"uid":68081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"可惜連登冇C打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b604a92ae6b528c906df10efc2606a96d338721","tid":2195913,"uid":128054,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"使唔使做到咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb13233e1e1f60ef4a3589c4f4fb21d2a18820ed","tid":2195913,"uid":128054,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"男人老狗學人嗌非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32608c4b96364227788841f207a9cc2f0dcbde4e","tid":219591